title: Credibility

steps.subtitle: Step One
steps.title: Consultation
steps.paragraph: We start by taking a deep dive into your business goals, processes and customers. Understanding your business allows us how we can best help by building a website that works towards your goals.

steps.subtitle: Step Two
steps.title: Design & Build
steps.paragraph: We'll start by designing a rough version of your website. We'll get feedback from you and create multiple iterations. Once you're happy, we'll start turning the design into a browsable website.

steps.subtitle: Step Three
steps.title: Launch Your New Website
steps.paragraph: We'll test your website on multiple devices, then we'll connect it to your domain and launch it for you at your desired time.
